{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351612829,"sessionID":"ses_31c036dcfffeZBZKwd7xzopNEA","part":{"id":"prt_ce3fe22980010u7INQBzve27If","sessionID":"ses_31c036dcfffeZBZKwd7xzopNEA","messageID":"msg_ce3fe19a0001N7MJC6ZIWQu19s","type":"text","text":"### Subtask 4: Fix features archive to use outputError() for JSON errors\n\nThe archive command uses `console.error`/`console.log` directly instead of `outputError()`. I need to add format support and use `outputError()` for error paths.","time":{"start":1773351612829,"end":1773351612829}}}
