{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351968170,"sessionID":"ses_31c036dcfffeZBZKwd7xzopNEA","part":{"id":"prt_ce40363ee002QXSx2cKudvrpwS","sessionID":"ses_31c036dcfffeZBZKwd7xzopNEA","messageID":"msg_ce4035ad6001kjfVC6hXBmxyI3","type":"text","text":"All 11 subtasks have been implemented and committed individually. Here's a summary of all changes:\n\n1. **`bug-enum-validation`** — Added `validateEnum()` calls in `features/add.ts` to reject invalid `--priority` and `--difficulty` values with clear error messages listing allowed values.\n\n2. **`bug-yaml-schema-crash`** — Added schema validation in `loadFeatures()` to check that `features` and `archive` are arrays (or null), not strings/objects. Provides clear error messages instead of crashing with \"Attempted to assign to readonly property\".\n\n3. **`bug-yaml-parse-error`** — Wrapped YAML parsing in a try-catch in `loadFeatures()` to emit `\"Failed to parse .features.yml: <reason>\"` instead of raw library errors.\n\n4. **`bug-archive-error-json`** — Converted `features archive` to use `outputError()` and `outputMessage()` from `output.ts` so errors output proper JSON when `--output json` is specified.\n\n5. **`bug-dev-mode-guard`** — Fixed the package name check from `\"wombo\"` to `\"wombo-combo\"` to match the actual `package.json` name.\n\n6. **`bug-stale-schema-version`** — Replaced hardcoded `\"0.0.2\"` in `allCommandSchemas()` with a dynamic `getVersion()` that reads from `package.json`.\n\n7. **`bug-version-flag-collision`** — Removed `--version` flag (which consumed the next arg), added `version` command with `-v`/`-V` shorthands, changed upgrade to use `--tag`/`--release` for version pinning.\n\n8. **`bug-trailing-flag-crash`** — Added `requireValue()` helper in `parseArgs` that checks bounds before consuming `args[++i]`. All value-consuming flags now emit clear `\"Flag --X requires a value\"` errors.\n\n9. **`bug-status-marks-dead-completed`** — Status command now checks `branchHasChanges()` before marking dead agents as completed. Agents that died without commits are marked `\"failed\"`.\n\n10. **`bug-dryrun-cleanup-matching`** — Replaced naive `line.includes(prefix)` worktree matching in dry-run cleanup with `listWomboWorktrees()` for safe basename-based filtering.\n\n11. **`bug-duration-parser-mismatch`** — Extended `parseDurationMinutes()` to support year/month durations with approximations (1Y=365D, 1M=30D), matching what the validator already accepted.","time":{"start":1773351968169,"end":1773351968169}}}
